address.streetAddress: FORRESTER Plan, The Parks of Carolina Forest

location.fullValue: FORRESTER Plan, The Parks of Carolina Forest

data.description: Welcome to this stylish 4-bedroom, 2 ½-bath residence, nestled within the highly desirable Parks of Carolina Forest. This impeccably designed home boasts a spacious kitchen with walk-in pantry, complemented by a versatile nook tucked beneath the staircase. The generous primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a luxurious ensuite bathroom with double sinks and an expansive walk-in closet. Step outside to discover a fenced, backyard oasis, ideal for both pets and family activities, complete with a cozy fire pit for memorable evenings. Residents of this community enjoy access to a wealth of amenities, including a resort-style swimming pool, fitness room, clubhouse, fire pit gathering area, and a delightful, discovery playground. Centrally located within Carolina Forest, this community offers the convenience of a quick golf cart ride to the amenity center, as well as proximity to a variety of dining options, grocery stores, gas stations, and numerous other conveniences. Experience both comfort and vibrant living in this Carolina Forest gem. Schedule a showing today!
